            <div xml:id="HerVoice"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="Free"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="love"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    <l>The wild bee reels from bough to bough</l>
                    <l>With his furry coat and his gauzy wing.</l> 
                    <l>Now in a lily-cup, and now</l>
                    <l>Setting a jacinth bell a -swing</l>
                    <l>In his wandering;</l>
                    <l>Sit closer love: it was here I trow</l>
                    <l>I made that vow,</l>
                    <l>Swore that two lives should be like one</l>
                    <l>As long as the sea-gull loved the sea,</l>
                    <l>As long as the sunflower sought the sun,-</l>
                    <l>It shall be, I said, for eternity</l>
                    <l>'Twixt you and me!</l>
                    <l>Dear friend, those times are over and done.</l>
                    <l>Love's web is spun.</l>
                    <l>Look upward where the polar trees</l>
                    <l>Sway in the summer air,</l>
                    <l>Here n the valley never a breeze</l>
                    <l>Scatters the thistledown, but there</l>
                    <l>Great winds blow fair</l>
                    <l>From the mighty murmuring mystical seas,</l>
                    
                    
